    "type": "message",
    "text": "Interesting, but it seems really draconian. Writing insufficient tests is far more subtle than sawing off your hand, it's like mismeasuring a mitre. Neophytes need to be allowed to make mistakes on little projects many many times as they acquire skills.\n\nA key part of bringing something new to people is being forgiving where possible.",
